We found an possible improvement idea which has caused at lot of trouble at customer side. In Issue search view the first found issue is selected when having list view enabled. If a user is now starting to type in a search term without selecting the search string bar first, he activates keyboard shortcuts by accident. This leads to various issues around this. The user could assign issues by accident to himself [i] without much notice. 

