h3. Problem Description

When users key in issue key in the description/comment (i.e ABC-1), JIRA will automatically render it with icon and status as updated at [What's New page|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/Cloud/What%27s+New#What'sNew-jiracore].
{quote}
Links to other JIRA issues (in the description or comments) are now rendered with an icon and status, rather than as just a plain hyperlink.
{quote}

h3. Suggested Solution

Provide an option to disable the auto render issue key with an icon and status.

h3. Workaround

When linking to issues use the link format instead of relying on automatic linking, for example:

{noformat}
[JRA-60814|https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRA-60814]
{noformat}

